%h1.h3.mb-3 New Consult OG

- meet_coming_soon = "Coming soon. For now, download any Google Meet transcript and upload or paste it below."
- zoom_coming_soon = "Coming soon. For now, download any Zoom transcript and upload or paste it below."

.card.mb-4
  .card-body
    %h5.mb-2 Zoom transcripts
    %p.small.text-muted.mb-3
      Direct import from Zoom is on the way. Until then, export a cloud recording transcript from Zoom and paste or upload it below.
    %span.d-inline-block{"tabindex" => "0", "data-bs-toggle" => "tooltip", "data-bs-title" => zoom_coming_soon}
      %button.btn.btn-outline-primary{type: "button", disabled: true, style: "pointer-events: none;"}
        %i.bi.bi-camera-video-fill.me-1
        Connect Zoom (transcripts)
        %span.badge.text-bg-secondary.ms-1 Coming soon

.card.mb-4
  .card-body
    %h5.mb-2 Google Meet transcripts
    %p.small.text-muted.mb-3
      Direct import from Google Meet is on the way. Until then, export a transcript from Meet and paste or upload it below.
    %span.d-inline-block{"tabindex" => "0", "data-bs-toggle" => "tooltip", "data-bs-title" => meet_coming_soon}
      %button.btn.btn-outline-primary{type: "button", disabled: true, style: "pointer-events: none;"}
        %i.bi.bi-camera-video.me-1
        Connect Google Meet (transcripts)
        %span.badge.text-bg-secondary.ms-1 Coming soon

%hr.my-4

= form_with model: @consult, url: organization_possible_observation_consults_path(organization), local: true, html: { multipart: true } do |f|
  .mb-3
    = f.label :display_name, "Name", class: "form-label"
    = f.text_field :display_name, class: "form-control", required: true
  .mb-3
    = f.label :source_text, "Paste transcript or notes", class: "form-label"
    = f.text_area :source_text, class: "form-control", rows: 12, placeholder: "Paste meeting notes or a transcript…"
  .mb-3
    = f.label :source_file, "Or upload a file (.txt, .vtt, .srt, .json, .csv)", class: "form-label"
    = f.file_field :source_file, class: "form-control", accept: ".txt,.vtt,.srt,.json,.csv,text/plain"
  - if @consult.errors.any?
    .alert.alert-danger
      %ul.mb-0
        - @consult.errors.full_messages.each do |msg|
          %li= msg
  .d-flex.gap-2
    = f.submit "Continue", class: "btn btn-primary"
    = link_to "Cancel", organization_possible_observation_consults_path(organization), class: "btn btn-outline-secondary"

%p.mt-3.small.text-muted
  Next you’ll confirm which teammates appear in this content. Then OG runs one consultation that can produce potential OGOs for all of them.
